{"tid":2341058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長者被虐或遭家庭暴力個案升逾一倍　自殺個案增五成","createTime":"2020-12-26T04:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T06:52:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"29d0dfde00cff32d6eef8bfa56b5db25276a2ad8","tid":2341058,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:53:56.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情出現近一年，長者安居協會行政總裁王虹虹在今天（26日）港台節目《香港家書》表示，疫情下長者是最脆弱的一群，過去一年協會處理的社工個案飆升，被虐或遭受家庭暴力的個案比過往上升超過一倍，自殺個案增加五成。<br />\n<br />\n王虹虹指，長者社交活動受阻導致抑鬱，他們和在家工作或失業的家人長期留在家，在擠逼環境增加磨擦，家庭問題越來越多。家人不讓他們出外。王虹虹表示，第四波爆發，未能紓緩日積月累的情緒和心理壓力可能會到臨界點，過去一年協會處理的社工個案飆升，被虐或遭受家庭暴力的個案比過往上升超過一倍，自殺個案增加五成。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01 .com/社會新聞/566552</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b78f4c0f1bc7e5732bf4664206ebadc5fa461243","tid":2341058,"uid":299311,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"依家啲xxx真係唔捱得<br />\n想當年我哋咪又係比人咁樣打大嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a35f75860549e90c9bfba076c31c6b41f804f22","tid":2341058,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"等睇又賴社會運動"},{"pid":"8dcb92020ba334a565f30893d4e0564f13807f9e","tid":2341058,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/shek-01_ULQc7_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fshek-01_ULQc7_1200x0.png&h=44056b06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa8b52d59bdca8ddb79f1bb702ae22526400c115","tid":2341058,"uid":54633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78f4c0f1bc7e5732bf4664206ebadc5fa461243","tid":2341058,"uid":299311,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"依家啲xxx真係唔捱得<br />\n想當年我哋咪又係比人咁樣打大嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/n